LIQUOR INDUSTRY -- CALIFORNIA; ALCOHOLIC BEVERAGES; PROPOSITION 134 (LIQUOR 
TAX); EXCISE TAX -- CALIFORNIA; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS 
</P>
