EMBASSIES; SPAIN -- EMBASSIES; REFUGEES -- CUBA; CUBA -- FOREIGN AID -- SPAIN; 
GRANTS; SUSPENSIONS; CUBA -- CELEBRATIONS; ANNIVERSARIES; SPEECHES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
