ORANGE COUNTY -- ATHLETICS; LIFESTYLES; QUIKSILVER INC; BILLABONG INTERNATIONAL 
LTD; OCEAN PACIFIC SWIMWEAR LTD; MAUI AND SONS (COMPANY); OFFSHORE OF 
CALIFORNIA (COMPANY) 
</P>
