POLITICAL CANDIDATES; SCHOOL BOARD ELECTIONS; SADDLEBACK VALLEY UNIFIED SCHOOL 
DISTRICT; CAPISTRANO UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT; SADDLEBACK COMMUNITY COLLEGE 
DISTRICT; LAGUNA BEACH UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT 
</P>
